bio:
As Global Account Leader in Life Sciences, part of the Industrial Manufacturing sector, I leverage Arcadis' key capabilities to deliver exceptional and sustainable outcomes for our clients. To achieve this I build effective relationships and I support and inspire colleagues to find the best solutions for our clients.

My Account Leader role combined with my previous experience in finance/audit enables me to have an in-depth understanding of our clients business challenges and needs to optimize their investments. 

I have a genuine interest in how the Life Sciences industry operates and in what is driving their business and growth. In Arcadis we have the proper propositions and solutions to sustain this growth, focusing on the core needs in the market:   
- Better and quicker delivery of capital expenditure projects; at a lesser cost (Capex); 
- Efficient and sustainable operations (Opex); 
- Compliant in a cost-effective way (Regulatory & Compliance); 
- Optimized and rightsized asset portfolio (M&A, divestments, asset swaps).

My focus areas, specialties & interests: 
Client Development; Account Management; Life Sciences Industry (incl. Pharmaceutical Industry); Agricultural & Agrochemical Industry; Industrial Manufacturing; Program Management; Tender Management in strategic pursuits; Business Strategy; Financial and audit expertise; Mergers & Acquisitions; University Teaching & Education
